review_title: PARFAIT CONTRE LA FROIDURE DU CANADA
reviews: Durant les temps froids de nos longs hivers canadiens, il faut s'habiller chaudement et les chemises flanelle sont prisées. Je devais renouveler mon vieux stock de chemises et je traversais une intense phase de paresse qui m'enleva le goût de magasiner au régional, j'ai donc tenté ma chance sur Amazon. J'ai commandé 4 chemises flanelle différentes en reprenant la taille L de mes anciens modèles. La livraison fut rapide et le produit était d'une qualité irréprochable. Taille conforme, pas de coutures malveillantes, pas de reboutages mal faits. La sainte perfection. Le produit est donc recommandable pour les grosses marmottes en hibernation.
product_name: Amazon Essentials mens Regular-fit Long-sleeve Plaid Flannel Shirt Button-Down Shirt

review_title: Perfect on reorder- buy your regular size.
reviews: Again, I sized up too far thinking that the shirts would be Chinese made and tiny, unfortunately the other shirt I ordered I couldn't return, so I bought this one in my husband's regular size, it fits perfectly and as expected. I'd buy your regular size and don't size up, on washing the other one didn't shrink so he may not be able to wear it, but I can use it for a barn shirt.

reviews: I was unexpectedly and pleasantly surprised at the quality of this item. reviews: I've been trying some pricier types of briefs lately and expected more from these. As soon as I tried them, I had major issues with the waistband rolling over. I've bought briefs with made with the same material at 1/4 the price that do a better job with the waistband. SAXX boats of how the seam is flat on the inside for a more comfortable feel but this means a comparatively bulky seam on the outside. if you're wearing light clothing, you tend to be aware of the seam. Again the 1/4 price briefs have a similar seam but its less obtrusive. I got some UA tech series briefs at, 1/2 the price of these that I consider to be infinitely superior.
product_name: Saxx Underwear Men's Boxer Briefs – Platinum Men’s Underwear – Boxer Briefs with Built-in Ballpark Pouch Support

review_title: I love Saxx underwear, but this one was way to large for the rated size..
reviews: Maybe it was a manufacture defect / wrong size tag, but I have purchased many saxx underwear and this one was much too loose for the size tag. All the medium briefs from Saxx fit pretty snug all aroung, but this one was very loose around the thighs and the man-package, which makes it pretty uncomfortable even with the amazing fabric.
product_name: Saxx Underwear Men's Boxer Briefs – Platinum Men’s Underwear – Boxer Briefs with Built-in Ballpark Pouch Support

review_title: Relaxed fit is a a bit too relaxed
reviews: The "Platinum" line is billed as a relaxed fit but I found them a bit loose even for that. Even a relaxed brief shouldn't bunch up under suit pants. They are great with sweats or for sleeping but I can't wear them with regular pants. That said the material is super soft and comfortable and I do like the "pouch". I went to one of their more fitted models and am much happier.
product_name: Saxx Underwear Men's Boxer Briefs – Platinum Men’s Underwear – Boxer Briefs with Built-in Ballpark Pouch Support

review_title: Fit is as intended, Size information may vary on individual preference
reviews:
The material is soft and the product feel and looks as intended. The front pouch for your "bits" is longer (bigger vertically) than other underwear style(s) of this type. This allows the user to put the product on and immediately all of your "bit" items fit right into place. This is a preference for the individual. With this style of product you do not need to adjust all of your "bits" to fit into a pouch. The pouch is long enough that everything fits in naturally. I like a loose fit and want all my "bits" to be held just slightly. This is the product for that.
If you are looking for a more snug fit in the thighs and "bits" area i would not suggest this product.
If you are a person that has to adjust your boxer/boxer briefs everytime you sit and stand, this is the product for you.
If you are looking for a little support with loose fit, this is the product for you.
I am roughly a 31-32 jean fit and i ordered the large, which is perfect for me. keep this in mind when ordering.
product_name: Saxx Underwear Men's Boxer Briefs – Platinum Men’s Underwear – Boxer Briefs with Built-in Ballpark Pouch Support

--> RIGHT!
product_name: Saxx Underwear Men's Boxer Briefs- Ultra Men’s Underwear- Boxer Briefs with Fly and Built-in Ballpark Pouch Support

review_title: Good for hot weather, sweat wicking, comfortable
reviews:
True to relaxed fit, good pouch room, I like the freedom of boxers but not the bunchy fabric. However a bit bunchy in the seat for me, so like some jeans I could go down a size in the waist (or get the slim version) even though the legs/pouch fit well.

Because of the two mesh sidewalls my stuff is always secured and never touching my legs. Some of the other pouch styles depending on your size, shape, and activities your doing - may slip out either through the pee hole or inside. Nice, soft, and like most modal doesn't keep sweat or odor. Thin which depending on your perspective either feels cheaper or more breathable.

If you're doing serious sports or running I'd get something more supportive. Its nice feeling and I love the patterns but also not life changing personally (I also haven't had severe chaffing issues or anything).
product_name: Saxx Underwear Men's Boxer Briefs- Ultra Men’s Underwear- Boxer Briefs with Fly and Built-in Ballpark Pouch Support

reviews: What a life changing price of fabric I’ll tell you what! The second you slip these over your twig and berries and you will notice the sun shines just a bit brighter just for you. If I could these would be all I would wear all day every day, buy it now it will change your life.

review_title: Purchase only if you're a size 9 or smaller.
reviews:
When these first arrived and I took them out of the packaging I was pleasantly surprised with the vibrant colours and detail on the stitching. For the price, I thought for sure 5-star rating. Then I tried to put them on. They say up to a size 12. I'm a size 12. These are not for a size 12 foot. Or for that matter an 11 or even a 10 I would suspect would have difficulties putting these on.

With some effort, stretching and what I can only imagine is the sound of sock-ruining tearing of fabric I was able to wiggle these child-sized things on. I'm expecting to get 2 or 3 uses out of them before they tear and have also noticed that after one wash cycle the vibrant colours are also fading away.

review_title: Fit is great, material is great
reviews: I wear size 10.5-11 US everything. These socks fit great, they might be a bit big for anyone in the 9 range though. Material is nice and soft, seams are good, colors are bright and consistent, they feel nice to wear. They are not too tight around the ankles which is also quite nice. I destroy socks quickly wearing duty boots all day so durability is yet to be seen, but I've been wearing holes clean through $15 per pair socks for too long. At 12 pairs for $30, I can stand to buy a few times a year and be WAYYYY ahead of where I was. Will likely be repeat buying as I need to!
product_name: WeciBor Men's Dress Cool Colorful Novelty Funny Casual Combed Cotton Crew Socks Pack

review_title: Socks are great but the "next day delivery" took 6 days & me going to the Purolator store to get it
reviews:
So, first I want to say that socks look very nice, the colours are wonderful and the quality is good. I have actually ordered 2 different packages from WeciBor and they have sent them right away, as it was supposed to be the next day delivery.

However, this is getting 1 star just because they have used the worst possible delivery service provider possible - Purolator. Without boring you with too many details, my delivery took 6 days (guess what - they don't work on the weekends) and it took me calling the Purolator three times and, in the end, me going to the Purolator store to get the package. Additionally, I was expecting some rather expensive sneakers today that I got from Brooks, also sent via Purolator; I've took the day off from work just to be home to prevent the delay that happened with these socks, and guess what - Purolator lost the package with the sneakers!

So, dear WeciBor please use a better delivery service in the future. Thank you!

review_title: Wear them in the morning and have holes by evening. Cheap Chinese quality
reviews:
These are the worst quality of socks that you can ever get. My socks usually last at least a year but not these ones.
I took a new pair from these, wore them in the morning and by the evening both of them had holes near the toes.
Took another pair the next morning thinking I should give them another chance and well, they had holes by the end of the day.

I have clean feet, almost no nails on my feet and have a desk job. This means I shouldn't have much wear and tear in socks and my usual socks last years. But not this one.

These are Chinese made and are probably the worst quality of socks that you can get.
